Les missions
Based on data modelling provided by IT, with a focus on business needs, extract and integrate both structured and unstructured data from various databases / data-stores :
Develop, test and implement the most suitable analytical models to identify meaningful patterns or trends from complex data sets and types;
Implement the annalytics pipeline against the business needs;
Analyse and improve regularly the accuracy of models against business needs;
Communicate findings through effective and easy-to-understand data visualisations adapted to the audience;
Be the interface between their functions, the data ecosystem and the requested solution;
Coach the function in the data-driven mind-set;
Actively contribute and share best practices, findings, and techniques with the wider data community.
Le profil
Le profil ingénieur est souhaité avec une expérience en BIG DATA , DATA Analyse...
Une bonne maîtrise de JAVA et SQL est souhaitée.
Dans le cadre de sa politique diversité, Manpower étudie, à compétences égales, toutes candidatures dont celles de personnes en situation de handicap

